title: Valerie - Anoraak, College & Minitel Rose Releases
description:
VALERIE STORY

Valerie is not only a blog, but a collective composed of music artists in the west of France (The Outrunners, College, Anoraak, Minitel Rose, Maethelvin and Russ Chimes).

With a strong drive and clear vision, Valerie is a medium in which these artists can share their influences and present their productions. <a href="

College - (2008) Secret Diary

College is the new cosmopolitan nu-disco outfit of David Grellier. His album features works with Minitel Rose, Electric Youth, and Anoraak and he is also founder of the record label Valerie.


Minitel Rose - (2008) The French Machine

Minitel Rose is an electro-disco trio originally from Nantes, France. The group is composed of Raphael, Romain and Quentin. Their premier album, The French Machine, was released in May of 2008.
